OL,3,CFortnum apologises after Paralympians
OL,4,Cnot invited to party after meeting King
OL,6,FFortnum & Mason has apologised for a
OL,7,F"failure of communication" to
OL,8,FParalympians who were not invited to a
OL,9,Fparty for Olympians after medallists
OL,10,Fmet the King.
OL,12,FBritish Olympians and Paralympians
OL,13,Fwere at Buckingham Palace on Thursday
OL,14,Fto celebrate the country's success in
OL,15,FParis this summer.
OL,17,FBut Zac Shaw, a visually impaired
OL,18,Fsprinter, said he was not invited to
OL,19,Fan after-party hosted by the luxury
OL,20,FLondon department store.
