OL,3,CFortnum apologises after Paralympians
OL,4,Cnot invited to party after meeting King
OL,6,FHe said he trawled through his emails
OL,7,Fto find an invite after one of his
OL,8,Ffriends, an Olympian, mentioned it to
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FNeither Mr Shaw nor his partner Ali
OL,12,FSmith, also a Paralympic sprinter,
OL,13,Fcould find an invite so the pair
OL,14,Fassumed it was an event for Olympians
OL,15,Fonly.
