OL,3,CFortnum apologises after Paralympians
OL,4,Cnot invited to party after meeting King
OL,6,FMr Shaw, who won silver in the mixed
OL,7,F4x100m and bronze in the 100m T12 in
OL,8,FParis, said it was "hurtful" and
OL,9,F"unfair" and an example of how the two
OL,10,Fsets of athletes are treated
OL,11,Fdifferently.
OL,13,FHe said: "It's just hurtful and I mean
OL,14,Fyou have situations like this honestly
OL,15,Fso frequently, whether it's brands,
OL,16,Fprize money, even hosting a Paralympic
OL,17,Frace at a competition.
OL,19,F"You have to pick your times to
OL,20,Factually call it out.
