OL,3,CFortnum apologises after Paralympians
OL,4,Cnot invited to party after meeting King
OL,6,F"There is a separate reception for
OL,7,FParalympians in the works here at
OL,8,FFortnum's which will be announced
OL,9,Fsoon," the message read.
OL,11,F"We are really sorry that we could not
OL,12,Fdo both of the planned parties
OL,13,Ftogether, which would have been our
OL,14,Fpreference, but we are restricted on
OL,15,Fspace and simply could not have fitted
OL,16,Feveryone in at the same time.
