OL,3,CFortnum apologises after Paralympians
OL,4,Cnot invited to party after meeting King
OL,6,F"However, there has been a failure of
OL,7,Fcommunication on our part here and we
OL,8,Fare truly sorry. We really hope to
OL,9,Fmake it up to you when we get everyone
OL,10,Ftogether to celebrate.
OL,12,F"Thank you for your patience and we
OL,13,Fwill get back to you personally with
OL,14,Fthe details soonest."
OL,16,FMr Shaw said the response was "not
OL,17,Fgood enough at all".
OL,19,FHe said he initially contacted Fortnum
OL,20,Fprivately but went public on social
OL,21,Fmedia when they did not respond.
