OL,3,CFortnum apologises after Paralympians
OL,4,Cnot invited to party after meeting King
OL,6,F"I just put a tweet out and didn't
OL,7,Fexpect anyone to interact with it," Mr
OL,8,FShaw said.
OL,10,F"It's been nice to see how many people
OL,11,Fwith disabilities or not have come to
OL,12,Fthe same conclusion that it's not
OL,13,Fequality."
OL,15,FFortnum & Mason was contacted for
OL,16,Ffurther comment.
